These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, cola, tea, fanta
4 different pets are kept: turtle, goldfish, bird, frog
1. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | mirinda | cola | fanta | tea |
| Pet        | turtle | goldfish   | frog | bird    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, romance, satire, sports
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, british, indonesian, thai
1. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the australian is on the left of the indonesian##1
3. the indonesian is in an odd position##4
4. the australian is the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the british is on the right of the indonesian##1
6. the australian is the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | adventure  | romance  | sports |
| Nationality   | thai    | australian | indonesian | british    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, corn, grapefruit, garlic
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, epic, scientific, family
1. the person eating garlic is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
2. the person eating grapefruit is in an even position##4
3. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
4. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
5. the person watching satire movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | garlic | grapefruit | corn    | kale      |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific        | family     | satire | epic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, collecting, rock-climbing, hiking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, punk, hip-hop, r&b
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the fan of techno and the fan of r&b##2
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
5. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | hiking | singing | collecting | rock-climbing |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop       | techno   | punk    | r&b  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, disco, salsa, indie
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, japanese, canadian, nigerian
1. the fan of salsa is on the right of the nigerian##1
2. the japanese is the fan of indie##1
3. the canadian is on the right of the fan of rock##1
4. the fan of disco is on the far left##1
5. the fan of salsa is in an odd position##4
6. the turkish is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | disco  | rock    | salsa   | indie       |
| Nationality   | turkish | nigerian | canadian | japanese |

