3. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
4. the argentine is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the australian is on the left or right of the argentine##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports      | horror | romance | martial-arts |
| Nationality   | british | indian     | argentine  | australian  |

