.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, disaster, satire, drama
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile, motorbike, bus
1. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
4. the person driving the bus is the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | drama | satire | disaster    |
| Transport     | bus | motorbike  | boat     | snowmobile |

