.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, journalist, entrepreneur, firefighter
4 different pets are kept: turtle, pony, dog, rat
1. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the journalist##3
2. the firefighter is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
4. the firefighter is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
5. the engineer is between the firefighter and the journalist##2
6. the owner of the pony is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the pony is between the engineer and the owner of the dog##2
8. the engineer is on the left or right of the journalist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | journalist | engineer      | firefighter | entrepreneur |
| Pet   | turtle  | rat | pony    | dog            |

