.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, plum, kale, carrot
4 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, dog, rat
1. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person eating artichoke##3
2. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating plum##1
3. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person eating kale##2
4. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating kale is the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | carrot | plum   | artichoke | kale |
| Pet    | rat     | chinchilla | bird     | dog  |

