.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate, tea, coffee
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, trance, pop, house
1. the person drinking milk is the fan of house##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
3. the fan of house is between the fan of reggae and the person drinking tea##2
4. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate       | tea   | milk | coffee |
| Music-Genre   | pop | trance | house        | reggae    |

