.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, cola, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, swimming, volleyball, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is rugby is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | mirinda   | soy-milk   | hot-chocolate      | cola      |
| Sport      | swimming | volleyball | skateboarding | rugby |

