.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: pepper, blueberry, peas, grapefruit
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, jazz, house, r&b
1. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of classical##1
2. the fan of house is in an even position##4
3. the person eating blueberry is in an even position##4
4. the person eating pepper is on the far right##1
5. the person eating peas is between the fan of jazz and the fan of house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | grapefruit | blueberry  | peas  | pepper |
| Music-Genre   | r&b  | house | classical | jazz   |

