.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, sports, epic, musical
4 different pets are kept: mouse, cat, rabbit, fish
1. the owner of the rabbit is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching horror movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
5. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
6. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | musical | horror | sports |
| Pet           | fish     | mouse     | rabbit   | cat         |

