.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, fishing, hiking, baking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, volleyball, rowing, rugby
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | baking | fishing         | sudoku   | hiking |
| Sport   | rowing    | volleyball | rugby | climbing   |

