.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, rock-climbing, video-games, drawing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, golf, climbing, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | hiking | video-games    | drawing |
| Sport   | tennis   | climbing  | biathlon | golf     |

