.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, puzzles, video-games, woodworking
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, indian, mexican, canadian
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an even position##4
3. the indian is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
4. the mexican is on the left or right of the indian##3
5. the indian is between the canadian and the mexican##2
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | woodworking   | video-games | camping | puzzles    |
| Nationality   | mexican | indian  | canadian     | chinese |

