.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, sprite, cola, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: papaya, garlic, cucumber, cranberry
1. the person eating garlic is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person eating cucumber is in an even position##4
7. the person eating papaya is the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | mirinda | lemonade    | cola       | sprite |
| Food       | garlic  | cucumber | cranberry | papaya  |

