.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, turkish, french, german
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, ship, airplane, helicopter
1. the malaysian is on the left of the german##1
2. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the right of the french##1
5. the malaysian is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
6. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | turkish | french | malaysian  | german |
| Transport     | scooter      | airplane       | ship | helicopter     |

