.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, architect, scientist, electrician
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, skateboard, quad-bike, car
1. the architect is in an even position##4
2. the architect is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
3. the person driving the skateboard is between the photographer and the person driving the taxi##2
4. the architect is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the electrician##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | photographer | scientist   | electrician | architect |
| Transport   | car          | skateboard | taxi         | quad-bike  |

 